# SEO Homepage Bundle Prompt

Use this template to generate a complete, SEO-optimized homepage content bundle.

---

## Prompt

Create a high-converting, SEO-optimized homepage content bundle for **[Business Name]**, a leading **[Business Type/Industry]** in **[City/Region]**.

---

## 1. Hero Section
- Write a strong headline (6–10 words) that includes **[primary keyword]**
- Add a compelling subheadline (1 sentence) featuring **[secondary keywords]** and **[unique value proposition]**
- Include a clear CTA button (2–4 words), e.g., **[Book Now / Get Started / Shop Now]**

---

## 2. Welcome Section (Max 2 sentences)
- Write a concise, engaging intro
- Naturally include **[primary keyword] + [location]**
- Mention **[core services/products]** and **[target audience]**
- Do NOT start with "Welcome to"
- Keep it inviting, clear, and benefit-driven

---

## 3. Value Proposition Bullets (3–5 bullets)
- Highlight key benefits such as:
  - **[Quality / Experience / Pricing / Speed / Trust]**
- Keep each bullet under 10 words
- Use action-oriented, customer-focused language

---

## 4. SEO CTA Section
- Write a persuasive call-to-action paragraph (1–2 sentences)
- Include **[primary keyword] + [location]**
- End with a strong CTA button label

---

## 5. Optional SEO Boost
- Add 3–5 keyword variations naturally within the content
- Keep tone aligned with **[brand voice: luxury / playful / corporate / family-friendly]**

---

## Output Requirements
- Keep everything concise and conversion-focused
- Avoid fluff and repetition
- Ensure natural keyword placement (no keyword stuffing)

---

